title.narrative: Funds being disbursed to grant holders via the fund manager

description.narrative: This activity (Funds being disbursed to grant holders via the fund manager) is a component of UK Aid Match 2013–2016: giving the public a say in how a portion of the aid budget is spent reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Not for profit organisation' and a budget of £31,232,910. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Multisector aid. , with the following implementing partners: MannionDaniels. The start date is 01-10-2013 and the end date is 30-12-2020.
